HEADWORD: Essene
<hw>Es*sene"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Essenes</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Gr. <?/, lit., physicians,
because they practiced medicine, fr. Chald <ets>⟦amac⟧say⟦amac⟧</ets> to
heal, cf. Heb. <ets>as⟦amac⟧</ets>.]</ety> <def>One of a sect among the
